<table border="0" cellpadding="5" width="550" cellspacing="5" height="400" >
<tr valign="top" height="400" >
<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style=""><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br>You elected to pay for your Kingsbridge business insurance policy&nbsp;<b>{!Policy__c.Name}&nbsp;</b>through direct debit payments.&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br>Our credit providers Close Brothers Premium Finance required some additional information from you as part of their ongoing Anti-Money Laundering requirements.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br>Close Brothers are required to identify all of their customers, but have been unable to do this through their automated process and need you to provide a copy of one of the following documents:</span></p><div style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><ul><li><font face="arial">Passport (valid and in date)</font></li><li><font face="arial">Valid Full/Provisional Photocard Driving License</font></li><li><font face="arial">National ID Card</font></li></ul></div><div style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="arial">Please send a photograph or scanned copy to us via email so Close Brothers can complete their checks.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></font><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>If Close Brothers are unable to complete their checks they may cancel your loan which would leave you with an outstanding balance which, if remained unpaid, could lead to the cancellation of your insurance policy.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>Please call us on&nbsp;<b>01242 808740</b>&nbsp;if you would like to discuss this matter further.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>Kind regards,<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>{!User.FirstName}<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Customer Service Team<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>E:&nbsp;</span><a href="mailto:customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk" style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk</a><br><span style="font-size: 12pt;">T: 01242 808 740</span></div>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>